  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Document Controller",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain and process company documents to ensure accurate and organized records throughout project phases</li><li>Assist project team by preparing reports, meeting notes, and fulfilling other documentation requests to support project progress</li><li>Manage and transmit project files from initiation through construction and closeout to maintain project continuity</li><li>Collect, scan, and upload documents following established procedures to ensure timely and accurate data entry</li><li>Register all technical documents, including reports, drawings, and blueprints, in the document management system for easy retrieval</li><li>Notify relevant personnel of updated document versions and provide guidance on accessing the latest information</li><li>Print and distribute documents as needed to facilitate communication and workflow across teams</li><li>Collaborate with various departments such as human resources, marketing, and construction to manage documents and records effectively</li></ul>",
